cellularAutomata.lib
Class Point

java.lang.Object
  cellularAutomata.lib.Point
Direct Known Subclasses:
Point1D, Point2D
public abstract class Point
extends java.lang.Object

An abstract representation of a point, that supports dimensions as large as the maximum array length. This class should be subclassed to represent a concrete dimension of point. Provided are 1D and 2D point classes, but this can be used to create points of more dimensions.

Author:
Kunal Desai, James Grugett, Prasanth Somasundar
